name: Alter Ego (itch) (VinayGupta23)
description:
Manage clones in this challenging 2D platformer that will tease both your mind and your reflexes!

Proudly designed by USC students as part of a course (Fall 2022), we can't wait for you to try our game and hear your comments!

If you're interested to connect, please reach Vinay Gupta on LinkedIn.
